  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bring Emotional Wellness to Schools during Covid</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project in Port Elizabeth, South Africa will restore emotional wellness to learners  at 180 local schools where Covid-19 and lockdown conditions have induced considerable fear, anxiety and stress. Children and youth are most traumatised, making learning extremely difficult. Over 6 workshop sessions, the Project will enable learners to express their feelings about Covid and strengthen their coping mechanisms. Those needing individual counselling will be identified and supported.</narrative>
  </description>
